  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        -  Diagnosis of COPD according to the European Respiratory Society (ERS) (R95-3225) and
             matching the following criteria:

               -  Stable moderate to severe airway obstruction

               -  Baseline 30 % &lt; FEV1 &lt; 65 % of European Community of Coal and Steel (ECCS)
                  predicted values (R94-1408).

               -  Baseline FEV1/SVC&lt; 70 %.

          -  Smoking history &gt; 10 pack-years (p.y.). A p.y. was defined as the equivalent of
             smoking

          -  One pack of cigarettes per day for one year.

          -  History of exacerbation in the past year.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
